stylometry: Probability distribution shows different outcomes and possibilities for a certain business-like decision to happen.  There are normal distributions which are a normal bell curve.  And there is also continuous distribution.  But, another probability distribution would be a discrete probability distribution.  A discrete probability distribution must be set up differently than any other probability distribution because of it's different qualities and characteristics. This distribution shows the likely hood of a certian outcome from happening, and is useful when trying to make a business-like decision.
